originalText.text: The CSS did my finger prints and helped me get my state and federal rap sheets for free. They provided me with Certificate of Goid Conduct application and guided me step-by-step on how to fill out the application. They have been super helpful answering questions. Their staff really accomplishes a lot. They’re also helpful providing references to other organizations that cover other needs. Everyone should have the CSS listed in the contacts.
